📋 Project Overview
HotelRevAI is an AI-powered analytics solution developed as part of the Infosys Springboard Internship (Batch 13, 8-Week Duration). The hospitality industry has long relied on static, season-based pricing models and manual intuition to manage room inventory and revenue. This approach consistently leads to two critical failures: underpricing during peak demand periods (leaving money on the table) and overpricing during low-demand periods (leaving rooms empty).

HotelRevAI directly addresses these inefficiencies by building an intelligent, data-driven system that analyzes historical booking records, market behavior, and guest patterns to make smarter, faster, and more profitable decisions. By leveraging machine learning algorithms and interactive Power BI dashboards, the platform transitions hotel management from a reactive mindset to a proactive revenue maximization strategy — optimizing RevPAR (Revenue Per Available Room) while maintaining strong occupancy rates across both City and Resort hotel types.

